- **Andy Grove** — Made semiconductors a global industry
- **Fei-Fei Li** — ImageNet — catalysed deep learning revolution

**Nobel & equivalent prize winners in your field**:
- **William Shockley, John Bardeen, Walter Brattain**: Invention of the transistor
- **Jack Kilby**: Invention of the integrated circuit
- **Isamu Akasaki, Hiroshi Amano, Shuji Nakamura**: Blue LED — enabling modern lighting
